00:17:45,270 --> 00:17:46,070
Your Majesty.

287
00:17:46,640 --> 00:17:47,440
Your Majesty.

288
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,240
Your Majesty!

289
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:51,200
You're killing the hounds
once the hare is caught!

290
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:53,920
If you kill us, your loyal subjects,

291
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,310
who will be left in the court

292
00:17:55,310 --> 00:17:58,590
to serve you, Your Majesty?

293
00:17:58,960 --> 00:17:59,760
About that...

294
00:17:59,830 --> 00:18:00,680
Your Majesty!

295
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:02,160
It's not your concern.

296
00:18:03,110 --> 00:18:04,160
Your Majesty!

297
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:05,980
Your Majesty!

298
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:07,280
Eunuch An.

299
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:11,690
Summon

300
00:18:11,960 --> 00:18:15,140
Senior Minister Xu to the hall.

301
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:18,860
Compared to what concerns
Lord Li and Lord Yang,

302
00:18:18,920 --> 00:18:20,190
I am more worried that,

303
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:22,640
since these two factions are
both made up of veteran officials,

304
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:24,000
if we uproot them all at once,

305
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:25,380
we young officials

306
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:27,090
may struggle to hold the court together.

307
00:18:27,090 --> 00:18:27,640
Exactly.

308
00:18:31,530 --> 00:18:33,250
It is time to invite him back

309
00:18:34,040 --> 00:18:35,200
to take charge.

310
00:18:56,270 --> 00:18:56,900
I am

311
00:18:57,610 --> 00:18:58,780
Xu Huaian.

312
00:18:59,070 --> 00:19:00,710
Greetings, Your Majesty.

313
00:19:01,310 --> 00:19:02,220
Wish you well,

314
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:03,720
Your Majesty.

315
00:19:17,520 --> 00:19:19,890
[The city fortifications
must be repaired immediately.]

316
00:19:34,990 --> 00:19:37,260
[Xiadu]

317
00:19:42,510 --> 00:19:44,570
The Three Armies rebelled this time,

318
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:46,960
fighting prefectural garrisons
all the way.

319
00:19:46,960 --> 00:19:49,160
Although we tried our best
to minimize casualties,

320
00:19:49,160 --> 00:19:51,030
many cities were still damaged.

321
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:52,740
I was thinking,

322
00:19:53,550 --> 00:19:55,150
while we're repairing them,

323
00:19:55,400 --> 00:19:57,720
why not sort out
the transportation infrastructure?

324
00:19:57,720 --> 00:19:58,310
Maybe

325
00:19:59,550 --> 00:20:00,590
we can really get Xie Yong'er's

326
00:20:00,590 --> 00:20:03,650
takeout and express delivery business
up and running.

327
00:20:09,070 --> 00:20:09,550
She...

328
00:20:12,110 --> 00:20:13,310
She is my best friend.

329
00:20:17,880 --> 00:20:19,010
Come and take a look.

330
00:20:19,750 --> 00:20:21,280
See where your hometown is.

331
00:20:38,930 --> 00:20:40,730
My hometown isn't here, either.

332
00:20:42,830 --> 00:20:43,430
It's okay.

333
00:20:44,510 --> 00:20:45,170
From now on,

334
00:20:46,070 --> 00:20:46,670
this place

335
00:20:47,440 --> 00:20:48,640
will be our hometown.

336
00:20:51,930 --> 00:20:53,400
Why are you still so thin?

337
00:20:55,000 --> 00:20:56,270
I'll tell the kitchen

338
00:20:56,550 --> 00:20:58,130
to make you two extra dishes every day.

339
00:20:58,130 --> 00:21:00,020
You're still growing.

340
00:21:00,050 --> 00:21:01,180
You need to eat well.

341
00:21:01,830 --> 00:21:02,240
Got it?

342
00:21:07,750 --> 00:21:08,440
Your Highness,

343
00:21:08,440 --> 00:21:10,040
Physician Xiao has arrived.

344
00:21:13,550 --> 00:21:14,410
Your Highness.

345
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:15,370
Physician Xiao.

346
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:16,540
Prince Duan...

347
00:21:17,960 --> 00:21:19,960
Xiahou Bo survived the amputation,

348
00:21:20,440 --> 00:21:22,160
but he still needs to break the fever
and wake up

349
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:23,620
before he's out of danger.

350
00:21:26,750 --> 00:21:28,410
He really is indestructible.

351
00:21:29,480 --> 00:21:30,080
By the way,

352
00:21:30,830 --> 00:21:32,880
about the "poison against poison" method
we discussed,

353
00:21:32,880 --> 00:21:34,410
have you made any progress?

354
00:21:34,550 --> 00:21:37,110
Regarding the two rare Qiang State poisons
in His Majesty's body,

355
00:21:37,110 --> 00:21:38,240
I have found the remnant

356
00:21:38,240 --> 00:21:39,900
of the ancient prescription,

357
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:41,200
but it is incomplete.

358
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:43,030
There are several ingredients

359
00:21:43,030 --> 00:21:44,480
with extremely strange names.

360
00:21:44,480 --> 00:21:46,080
As for what they actually are

361
00:21:46,310 --> 00:21:48,000
or whether they exist in the Great Xia,

362
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:49,330
I have no way of knowing.

363
00:21:52,260 --> 00:21:53,120
Your Highness,

364
00:21:53,640 --> 00:21:56,840
could you send someone
to the Qiang State to investigate?

365
00:21:58,440 --> 00:21:59,450
A round trip

366
00:22:00,480 --> 00:22:02,080
would take at least 3 months.

367
00:22:02,440 --> 00:22:04,900
I'm afraid His Majesty
can't wait that long.

368
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:06,440
Physician Xiao,

369
00:22:06,440 --> 00:22:08,440
can you deduce
the effects of the ingredients

370
00:22:08,440 --> 00:22:10,570
and find substitutes in the Great Xia?

371
00:22:10,790 --> 00:22:11,850
Given enough time,

372
00:22:11,960 --> 00:22:12,760
perhaps I can.

373
00:22:13,590 --> 00:22:14,790
"Given enough time"?

374
00:22:15,680 --> 00:22:16,610
At least 3 years.

375
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:22,640
I will send a message to Tu'er right now.

376
00:22:23,310 --> 00:22:24,710
Let's hope for a miracle.

377
00:22:34,200 --> 00:22:35,060
Your Highness,

378
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:37,860
regarding Consort Xie...

379
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:41,400
Did she leave the palace successfully?

380
00:22:46,750 --> 00:22:48,210
After she left the palace,

381
00:22:49,720 --> 00:22:50,650
we lost contact.

382
00:22:54,740 --> 00:22:55,730
Before she left,

383
00:22:57,920 --> 00:22:58,590
she said

384
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:02,300
she was going home.

385
00:23:06,920 --> 00:23:07,650
That is good.

386
00:23:08,070 --> 00:23:08,800
That is good.

387
00:23:12,750 --> 00:23:14,710
If it is convenient, Your Highness,

388
00:23:14,710 --> 00:23:16,400
please tell Consort Xie

389
00:23:18,310 --> 00:23:19,970
that I have been looking after

390
00:23:21,310 --> 00:23:23,170
the two angelica plants she left.

391
00:23:24,670 --> 00:23:25,870
Tell her not to worry.

392
00:23:31,790 --> 00:23:32,990
I shall take my leave.

393
00:23:33,720 --> 00:23:34,180
Hold on.

394
00:23:40,110 --> 00:23:41,440
Before Yong'er set off,

395
00:23:42,560 --> 00:23:43,960
she left a letter for you.

396
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:49,600
For me?

397
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:03,960
Tiny Genius.

398
00:24:05,510 --> 00:24:07,640
I remember your surprised expression

399
00:24:07,790 --> 00:24:09,480
when I called you this for the first time.

400
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:11,080
It feels like a lifetime ago.

401
00:24:11,590 --> 00:24:12,480
May I have

402
00:24:12,830 --> 00:24:14,070
your name, Imperial Physician?

403
00:24:14,070 --> 00:24:15,550
My name is Xiao Tiancai.

404
00:24:16,550 --> 00:24:17,640
Tiny Genius?

405
00:24:18,340 --> 00:24:20,550
You didn't understand
what I meant back then.

406
00:24:20,550 --> 00:24:21,550
I also didn't know

407
00:24:21,880 --> 00:24:23,270
that you would be the first person

408
00:24:23,270 --> 00:24:26,000
in this palace
who would truly help and accept me.

409
00:24:27,480 --> 00:24:29,940
In the countless times
I brushed with death,

410
00:24:30,530 --> 00:24:32,460
it was you who fought to get me back.

411
00:24:33,720 --> 00:24:35,250
Hope I still have the chance

412
00:24:35,510 --> 00:24:37,970
to express the gratitude
I owe you in person.

413
00:24:39,900 --> 00:24:41,190
When the dust settles,

414
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:42,680
if I hear about your visit,

415
00:24:42,680 --> 00:24:44,550
I will definitely restore the old bond

416
00:24:44,550 --> 00:24:45,880
and resume our romance.

417
00:24:46,310 --> 00:24:47,110
From Yong'er.

418
00:24:57,030 --> 00:24:58,490
Thank you, Your Highness.

419
00:25:00,640 --> 00:25:01,840
I shall take my leave.

420
00:25:10,670 --> 00:25:11,240
Yong'er.

421
00:25:12,850 --> 00:25:15,110
Just let him think you're out of contact,

422
00:25:15,640 --> 00:25:16,840
wandering the world.

423
00:25:19,590 --> 00:25:21,850
Leave him with a glimmer of hope forever.

424
00:26:22,270 --> 00:26:23,070
What's wrong?

425
00:26:24,510 --> 00:26:25,910
Did you have a nightmare?

426
00:26:27,480 --> 00:26:28,350
Do you remember

427
00:26:29,050 --> 00:26:30,270
when we first met,

428
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:31,110
I said

429
00:26:32,060 --> 00:26:34,110
the tyrant in "Devil's Favorite Concubine"

430
00:26:34,110 --> 00:26:36,770
died in an assassination
at the end of the story?

431
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:39,330
I know who the assassin was now.

432
00:26:39,550 --> 00:26:40,150
Who was it?

433
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:42,330
The original Yu Wanyin

434
00:26:42,680 --> 00:26:44,340
tried to win Prince Duan back,

435
00:26:44,350 --> 00:26:45,150
so she ended up

436
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:49,020
assassinating the Emperor
with a poisoned dagger.

437
00:26:49,630 --> 00:26:50,190
It was me.

438
00:26:51,090 --> 00:26:51,890
I killed you.

439
00:26:58,830 --> 00:26:59,400
Wanyin.

440
00:27:01,790 --> 00:27:03,990
That was the plot of the original novel.

441
00:27:05,960 --> 00:27:07,090
Xie Yong'er is dead.

442
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:09,970
Xiahou Bo is crippled, too.

443
00:27:10,070 --> 00:27:11,600
We've nipped

444
00:27:12,240 --> 00:27:13,920
all the disasters in the bud.

445
00:27:15,160 --> 00:27:16,490
We've changed our fate.

446
00:27:16,880 --> 00:27:18,920
But the Nameless's letter emphasized

447
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:20,790
that when two stars meet,
one is destined to fall.

448
00:27:20,790 --> 00:27:21,590
What he said is

449
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:23,480
just some meaningless crap.

450
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:24,720
How could it be crap?

451
00:27:25,310 --> 00:27:26,820
He predicted our arrival

452
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:28,180
and Mr. Bei's death.

453
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:29,700
He predicted everything.

454
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:31,580
Ignore him.

455
00:27:32,200 --> 00:27:33,460
He's just a charlatan.

456
00:27:34,350 --> 00:27:34,850
Look.

457
00:27:35,270 --> 00:27:36,920
What about the five stars align

458
00:27:36,920 --> 00:27:38,120
he mentioned before?

459
00:27:40,110 --> 00:27:41,310
Didn't we get over it?

460
00:27:43,320 --> 00:27:43,830
Don't overthink it.

461
00:27:43,830 --> 00:27:44,960
Five stars align...

462
00:27:47,240 --> 00:27:48,370
Where are you going?

463
00:27:49,410 --> 00:27:50,610
At least put on a coat.

464
00:27:58,550 --> 00:28:00,110
The last time I saw them,

465
00:28:01,960 --> 00:28:03,560
their tails were still bent.

466
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:06,890
I thought

467
00:28:06,980 --> 00:28:08,200
this ordeal was over.

468
00:28:08,920 --> 00:28:09,780
But it turns out

469
00:28:12,920 --> 00:28:14,160
that it's yet to come.

470
00:28:25,380 --> 00:28:29,070
[Half a month later]

471
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:40,720
Why are all these officials

472
00:28:40,720 --> 00:28:42,500
coming to meet Her Highness lately?

473
00:28:42,500 --> 00:28:43,920
His Majesty is critically ill.

474
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:45,610
There must be someone
to handle state affairs.

475
00:28:45,610 --> 00:28:46,920
And the medicine is also

476
00:28:46,920 --> 00:28:48,790
sent to the Yongyan Hall jar after jar.

477
00:28:48,790 --> 00:28:50,350
Her Highness supervises
the brewing herself.

478
00:28:50,350 --> 00:28:52,150
She didn't even have time to eat.

479
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:55,360
If anything happens to His Majesty,

480
00:28:55,790 --> 00:28:56,460
the palace

481
00:28:56,750 --> 00:28:58,350
can't withstand any more chaos.

482
00:28:58,350 --> 00:28:59,720
Don't say that recklessly!

483
00:28:59,720 --> 00:29:00,650
Get back to work.

484
00:29:04,270 --> 00:29:05,130
Your Highness.

485
00:29:06,070 --> 00:29:07,440
About returning fields to the people,

486
00:29:07,440 --> 00:29:09,240
there is still some dispute in the court.

487
00:29:09,240 --> 00:29:09,830
Should we

488
00:29:10,110 --> 00:29:11,720
delay it for a while?

489
00:29:13,030 --> 00:29:13,490
No need.

490
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:16,200
Proceed as previously planned.

491
00:29:16,720 --> 00:29:17,980
Ask whoever opposes it

492
00:29:18,160 --> 00:29:19,720
go home and reflect on themselves.

493
00:29:19,720 --> 00:29:20,450
Understood.

494
00:29:21,240 --> 00:29:22,100
Your Highness,

495
00:29:22,550 --> 00:29:23,880
I am already working on reopening

496
00:29:23,880 --> 00:29:25,410
the special imperial exam.

497
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:27,020
But currently,

498
00:29:27,110 --> 00:29:28,680
we are short of personnel in the court.

499
00:29:28,680 --> 00:29:29,340
Therefore,

500
00:29:29,720 --> 00:29:32,430
Senior Minister Xu has drafted
a list of candidates.

501
00:29:32,430 --> 00:29:35,630
He asked me to present it
to you for review, Your Highness.

502
00:29:40,200 --> 00:29:41,240
Qiu Guangzhi.

503
00:29:42,270 --> 00:29:43,200
Song Yubin.

504
00:29:44,270 --> 00:29:45,000
Luo Shu.

505
00:29:46,590 --> 00:29:48,000
I have read their essays.

506
00:29:48,750 --> 00:29:50,480
Please tell Senior Minister Xu

507
00:29:50,480 --> 00:29:51,830
to appoint them exceptionally.

508
00:29:51,830 --> 00:29:52,560
Understood.

509
00:29:57,960 --> 00:29:58,680
Lord Er,

510
00:29:59,550 --> 00:30:01,280
do you have anything to report?

511
00:30:01,830 --> 00:30:03,680
She's about to resign
and live in seclusion.

512
00:30:03,680 --> 00:30:05,410
What else would she have to say?

513
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:08,060
You are resigning?

514
00:30:11,670 --> 00:30:12,560
Your Highness,

515
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:14,500
I am a woman.

516
00:30:14,720 --> 00:30:17,180
Although it's only
between a few of us for now,

517
00:30:17,180 --> 00:30:18,640
it's still improper for me

518
00:30:19,200 --> 00:30:20,110
to serve in the court.

519
00:30:20,110 --> 00:30:21,170
How is it improper?

520
00:30:21,830 --> 00:30:24,160
Wasting a talent
who can benefit the people is

521
00:30:24,160 --> 00:30:25,490
what's truly improper.

522
00:30:25,750 --> 00:30:26,280
Exactly.

523
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:28,680
Besides, with His Majesty
and Her Highness here,

524
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:30,880
no one in the court would dare to gossip.

525
00:30:32,110 --> 00:30:33,970
Thank you both for your kindness.

526
00:30:34,310 --> 00:30:36,110
But I've made up my mind to leave.

527
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:40,080
I hope you can
grant my request, Your Highness.

528
00:30:50,270 --> 00:30:50,790
Lord Er,

529
00:30:51,740 --> 00:30:53,470
could you wait a little longer?

530
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:55,160
The court is understaffed right now,

531
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:56,590
and His Majesty is critically ill.

532
00:30:56,590 --> 00:30:58,720
Why don't we give ourselves some time,

533
00:30:59,420 --> 00:31:01,280
wait until His Majesty recovers,

534
00:31:01,680 --> 00:31:03,080
and then make a decision?

535
00:31:26,550 --> 00:31:27,410
Your Highness.

536
00:31:29,030 --> 00:31:29,960
Physician Xiao,

537
00:31:30,160 --> 00:31:31,360
where is General Lin?

538
00:31:31,440 --> 00:31:33,590
General Lin went out of the city
to look for herbs.

539
00:31:33,590 --> 00:31:34,820
He said the Nameless's divination

540
00:31:34,820 --> 00:31:35,680
can't be wrong.

541
00:31:36,110 --> 00:31:37,750
Since the divination says
he can save His Majesty,

542
00:31:37,750 --> 00:31:39,410
then he certainly can make it.

543
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:40,640
How is His Majesty...

544
00:31:41,070 --> 00:31:41,980
How is he doing?

545
00:31:42,350 --> 00:31:44,350
He had two more episodes last night.

546
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:46,530
He took the medicine as you instructed

547
00:31:46,750 --> 00:31:48,550
and is currently in a deep sleep.

548
00:31:49,900 --> 00:31:52,310
Why is his condition
deteriorating so fast?

549
00:31:52,310 --> 00:31:54,200
He was able to attend court
just a couple of days ago.

550
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:56,960
His Majesty's condition is
somewhat similar to Cen Jintian's.

551
00:31:56,960 --> 00:31:58,690
Now that everything is settled

552
00:31:59,270 --> 00:32:01,000
and all obstacles are removed,

553
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:03,200
the will
that was holding His Majesty up is

554
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:03,790
gone.

555
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:07,920
How long does he have?

556
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:09,250
This poison in the blood

557
00:32:09,720 --> 00:32:11,850
has affected His Majesty's mobility.

558
00:32:12,790 --> 00:32:13,440
He may be

559
00:32:14,110 --> 00:32:16,370
unable to move in the next couple of days.

560
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:17,830
Delirium will follow.

561
00:32:19,030 --> 00:32:19,640
At most...

562
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:25,000
At most, he has 10 to 15 days left.

563
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:28,740
Your Highness.

564
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:31,000
In that case,

565
00:32:32,780 --> 00:32:33,710
Physician Xiao,

566
00:32:34,550 --> 00:32:36,080
please increase his dosage

567
00:32:36,720 --> 00:32:38,920
and keep him asleep as much as possible.

568
00:32:38,920 --> 00:32:40,120
Don't let him suffer.

569
00:32:41,070 --> 00:32:41,800
Understood.

570
00:32:47,310 --> 00:32:49,570
Won't you go in to see him, Your Highness?

571
00:32:49,720 --> 00:32:52,120
He said he wants me
to remember him as he was,

572
00:32:53,060 --> 00:32:54,120
not as he is now.

573
00:32:56,880 --> 00:32:57,940
I respect his wish.

574
00:33:23,240 --> 00:33:24,510
When two stars meet,

575
00:33:25,110 --> 00:33:26,440
one is destined to fall.

576
00:33:27,380 --> 00:33:28,770
Five stars align,

577
00:33:34,470 --> 00:33:36,600
amidst despair, great fortune rises.

578
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:40,550
For this world,

579
00:33:41,400 --> 00:33:42,820
losing a mad king

580
00:33:43,510 --> 00:33:44,640
to gain an empress is

581
00:33:46,400 --> 00:33:47,330
quite a bargain.

582
00:33:48,390 --> 00:33:49,610
Don't talk nonsense.

583
00:33:51,000 --> 00:33:54,270
Only surviving counts
as "amidst despair, great fortune rises."

584
00:33:54,270 --> 00:33:54,880
Wanyin.

585
00:33:57,550 --> 00:33:59,080
Everyone dies eventually.

586
00:34:00,440 --> 00:34:01,900
Instead of losing my mind,

587
00:34:03,110 --> 00:34:05,390
wailing for days before I pass away,

588
00:34:07,960 --> 00:34:09,560
I'd rather die a quick death.

589
00:34:10,280 --> 00:34:11,210
What do you mean?

590
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:15,489
You want me to kill you with my own hands

591
00:34:16,230 --> 00:34:17,760
like in the original novel?

592
00:34:20,699 --> 00:34:21,679
Of course not.

593
00:34:24,070 --> 00:34:24,760
I just don't want

594
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:26,219
to leave you my worst side.

595
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:28,920
So you knew it all along, didn't you?

596
00:34:29,150 --> 00:34:31,250
You knew only one of us could survive.

597
00:34:32,969 --> 00:34:34,949
How could you be so cruel to me?

598
00:34:39,550 --> 00:34:41,750
You told me you wouldn't leave me alone.

599
00:34:42,760 --> 00:34:43,760
You lied to me.

600
00:34:45,699 --> 00:34:46,679
If I'd known,

601
00:34:47,699 --> 00:34:48,690
♪ Tell me ♪

602
00:34:48,760 --> 00:34:51,030
you should have kicked me
out of the palace in the first place,

603
00:34:49,350 --> 00:34:52,810
♪ Why so many laments echo in the wind ♪

604
00:34:51,670 --> 00:34:53,670
or I should have come after you died.

605
00:34:54,420 --> 00:34:55,570
♪ Walk past me ♪

606
00:34:55,870 --> 00:34:59,570
♪ Like an aloof passerby ♪

607
00:34:56,710 --> 00:34:58,390
I wish I'd never met you.

608
00:34:58,670 --> 00:35:00,800
I wish I'd never eaten hot pot with you.

609
00:35:00,800 --> 00:35:02,280
I wish I'd never fallen for your tricks.

610
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:03,500
♪ Don't watch me as the rain falls ♪

611
00:35:02,280 --> 00:35:04,210
I wish I'd never read your letters.

612
00:35:04,270 --> 00:35:07,000
♪ Love burns too hot as it passes ♪

613
00:35:07,820 --> 00:35:13,520
♪ Even a lifetime of war
cannot be extinguished ♪

614
00:35:14,630 --> 00:35:15,760
♪ Blame me ♪

615
00:35:16,420 --> 00:35:19,910
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

616
00:35:21,480 --> 00:35:22,760
♪ Hide me ♪

617
00:35:23,170 --> 00:35:27,080
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

618
00:35:23,880 --> 00:35:25,080
But fortunately,

619
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:27,880
our Empress is

620
00:35:28,320 --> 00:35:30,790
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

621
00:35:28,750 --> 00:35:29,950
so magnanimous

622
00:35:31,440 --> 00:35:32,880
that she will repay malice with kindness,

623
00:35:31,650 --> 00:35:34,320
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

624
00:35:33,880 --> 00:35:35,190
follow the will of Heaven and the people,

625
00:35:35,190 --> 00:35:38,180
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

626
00:35:36,880 --> 00:35:38,030
and reign for ages.

627
00:35:38,260 --> 00:35:40,320
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

628
00:35:40,510 --> 00:35:41,400
No, I don't want it.

629
00:35:40,710 --> 00:35:43,090
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

630
00:35:42,030 --> 00:35:42,760
Without you,

631
00:35:43,070 --> 00:35:44,030
I can't go on.

632
00:35:43,150 --> 00:35:45,020
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

633
00:35:45,050 --> 00:35:47,520
♪ I never yielded ♪

634
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:46,190
You can do it

635
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:49,300
♪ But why ♪

636
00:35:47,880 --> 00:35:48,760
Bai told me.

637
00:35:49,570 --> 00:35:54,060
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

638
00:35:51,110 --> 00:35:53,020
Before I came back,

639
00:35:53,040 --> 00:35:53,850
you could

640
00:35:54,480 --> 00:35:56,850
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

641
00:35:54,550 --> 00:35:55,840
hold your own, right?

642
00:35:56,900 --> 00:35:58,700
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

643
00:35:58,770 --> 00:36:01,080
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

644
00:35:58,840 --> 00:36:00,840
You'll do even better in the future.

645
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:03,320
♪ The first time I met you ♪

646
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:02,560
Don't cry.

647
00:36:03,670 --> 00:36:12,620
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

648
00:36:05,090 --> 00:36:06,190
I apologize to you.

649
00:36:07,510 --> 00:36:08,030
Okay?

650
00:36:11,710 --> 00:36:13,910
If reincarnation exists in this world,

651
00:36:16,110 --> 00:36:16,800
I will repay

652
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:21,060
what I owe you in the next life.

653
00:36:22,150 --> 00:36:23,610
I don't want the next life.

654
00:36:24,150 --> 00:36:25,510
I want this life.

655
00:36:26,550 --> 00:36:27,680
♪ Blame me ♪

656
00:36:27,710 --> 00:36:28,810
I want you to stay

657
00:36:28,320 --> 00:36:31,820
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

658
00:36:29,510 --> 00:36:30,550
by my side.

659
00:36:33,440 --> 00:36:34,500
♪ Hide me ♪

660
00:36:35,180 --> 00:36:38,980
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

661
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:37,730
I want to stay more than anyone.

662
00:36:40,310 --> 00:36:42,760
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

663
00:36:43,680 --> 00:36:46,240
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

664
00:36:47,240 --> 00:36:50,220
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

665
00:36:47,380 --> 00:36:48,920
But I have no choice.

666
00:36:50,240 --> 00:36:52,340
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

667
00:36:52,810 --> 00:36:55,230
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

668
00:36:55,280 --> 00:36:57,040
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

669
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:56,480
Wanyin...

670
00:36:57,070 --> 00:36:59,590
♪ I never yielded ♪

671
00:36:59,230 --> 00:37:00,270
If I die,

672
00:36:59,900 --> 00:37:01,420
♪ But why ♪

673
00:37:01,630 --> 00:37:06,120
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

674
00:37:02,190 --> 00:37:04,590
I can return to the world
outside the novel.

675
00:37:06,190 --> 00:37:07,580
I will definitely go find you then.

676
00:37:06,530 --> 00:37:08,890
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

677
00:37:08,930 --> 00:37:10,780
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

678
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:11,840
If I can't go back...

679
00:37:10,830 --> 00:37:13,150
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

680
00:37:13,620 --> 00:37:15,320
♪ The first time I met you ♪

681
00:37:15,910 --> 00:37:18,830
♪ There was once light ♪

682
00:37:17,230 --> 00:37:18,970
Please remember me as I am now.

683
00:37:19,410 --> 00:37:27,790
♪ In my soul ♪

684
00:37:23,360 --> 00:37:24,960
Let's say goodbye properly.

685
00:37:27,870 --> 00:37:29,430
I don't want to.

686
00:37:33,890 --> 00:37:36,310
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

687
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:38,230
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

688
00:37:38,250 --> 00:37:40,720
♪ I never yielded ♪

689
00:37:41,010 --> 00:37:42,480
♪ But why ♪

690
00:37:42,800 --> 00:37:47,400
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

691
00:37:47,710 --> 00:37:50,070
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

692
00:37:49,670 --> 00:37:51,510
If one of us has to die,

693
00:37:50,110 --> 00:37:51,960
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

694
00:37:52,010 --> 00:37:54,330
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

695
00:37:53,920 --> 00:37:55,030
it could be me.

696
00:37:54,740 --> 00:37:56,510
♪ The first time I met you ♪

697
00:37:57,040 --> 00:38:04,930
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

698
00:38:00,400 --> 00:38:01,260
Your Highness,

699
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:02,940
it's getting late.

700
00:38:03,260 --> 00:38:04,320
Please rest early.

701
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:24,620
Your Highness.

702
00:38:25,510 --> 00:38:26,000
Twelve?

703
00:38:27,030 --> 00:38:28,090
What's the matter?

704
00:38:28,150 --> 00:38:29,010
Your Highness.

705
00:38:29,440 --> 00:38:30,420
That mute girl

706
00:38:30,510 --> 00:38:33,170
tried to sneak
into the small pharmacy just now.

707
00:38:37,630 --> 00:38:39,030
The small pharmacy was

708
00:38:39,440 --> 00:38:41,240
remodeled specifically to hide

709
00:38:41,280 --> 00:38:42,670
His Majesty's illness.

710
00:38:43,280 --> 00:38:44,540
It's heavily guarded.

711
00:38:45,280 --> 00:38:48,010
There's no way
ordinary maids can get close to it.

712
00:38:48,280 --> 00:38:49,680
What was she doing there?

713
00:38:49,710 --> 00:38:50,550
I do not know.

714
00:38:51,110 --> 00:38:51,980
She is cunning.

715
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:54,320
She seemed to know
where the other secret guards were

716
00:38:54,320 --> 00:38:55,760
and moved extremely fast.

717
00:38:55,760 --> 00:38:57,760
Only I was newly added to today's shift,

718
00:38:57,760 --> 00:38:59,230
and so was my post.

719
00:38:59,400 --> 00:39:00,600
She did not know that,

720
00:39:00,630 --> 00:39:02,090
so I spotted her movement.

721
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:03,590
How is it on His Majesty's side?

722
00:39:03,590 --> 00:39:04,800
Don't worry, Your Highness.

723
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:06,590
The side hall is impregnable right now.

724
00:39:06,590 --> 00:39:07,650
No one can sneak in.

725
00:39:08,280 --> 00:39:09,140
Just to be safe,

726
00:39:09,670 --> 00:39:11,550
tell the side hall to pour out
all the medicine sent

727
00:39:11,550 --> 00:39:12,630
by the small pharmacy today

728
00:39:12,630 --> 00:39:13,880
and brew it over again.

729
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:14,610
Understood.

730
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:47,510
I still have a lot to do,

731
00:39:47,880 --> 00:39:48,740
so I'll skip it.

732
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:02,660
Isn't that what I said before?

733
00:40:54,320 --> 00:40:54,800
Help...

734
00:40:55,960 --> 00:40:56,820
Someone, help.

735
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:02,770
Flower,

736
00:41:03,480 --> 00:41:03,880
hurry.

737
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:06,080
Fetch me an imperial physician.

738
00:41:06,190 --> 00:41:07,190
I don't feel well.

739
00:41:10,920 --> 00:41:11,900
It is pointless.

740
00:41:12,320 --> 00:41:13,360
You are poisoned.

741
00:41:19,880 --> 00:41:20,360
You...

742
00:41:22,030 --> 00:41:23,080
You can speak?

743
00:41:31,710 --> 00:41:32,550
That soup.

744
00:41:35,120 --> 00:41:36,250
All day today,

745
00:41:37,480 --> 00:41:39,530
I only ate the soup you brought me.

746
00:41:41,190 --> 00:41:42,520
Take me to the pharmacy.

747
00:41:42,920 --> 00:41:44,180
Once the Emperor dies,

748
00:41:44,400 --> 00:41:45,930
I'll give you the antidote,

749
00:41:46,070 --> 00:41:47,200
and you can survive.

750
00:41:49,280 --> 00:41:50,880
You are from the Qiang State?

751
00:41:50,920 --> 00:41:51,280
Yes.

752
00:41:52,840 --> 00:41:54,500
You entered the palace with me

753
00:41:55,150 --> 00:41:56,550
just to assassinate him?

754
00:41:57,110 --> 00:41:57,910
That is right.

755
00:41:59,510 --> 00:42:01,320
But after you entered the palace,

756
00:42:01,320 --> 00:42:03,050
your clothes were all changed.

757
00:42:03,880 --> 00:42:05,480
Where did you get the poison?

758
00:42:07,280 --> 00:42:07,830
Heaven is

759
00:42:09,070 --> 00:42:10,050
helping me.

760
00:42:11,550 --> 00:42:12,500
What do you mean?

761
00:42:13,510 --> 00:42:15,040
You only have 2 hours left.

762
00:42:15,550 --> 00:42:16,550
If we don't go now,

763
00:42:16,840 --> 00:42:17,960
you will die.

764
00:42:22,150 --> 00:42:23,200
I cannot do it.

765
00:42:24,280 --> 00:42:27,230
All of His Majesty's food
and drink is specifically checked.

766
00:42:27,230 --> 00:42:29,190
Even if I put poison in the medicine,

767
00:42:29,190 --> 00:42:31,150
the imperial physician will find it out.

768
00:42:31,150 --> 00:42:31,960
He trusts you.

769
00:42:32,590 --> 00:42:33,590
He won't check the medicine

770
00:42:33,590 --> 00:42:34,320
you give him.

771
00:42:36,030 --> 00:42:38,150
His Majesty does not have long to live.

772
00:42:38,150 --> 00:42:39,550
Why go to such trouble?

773
00:42:40,920 --> 00:42:41,780
My parents were

774
00:42:42,030 --> 00:42:43,370
the Queen's warriors.

775
00:42:43,510 --> 00:42:45,110
But the Emperor killed them.

776
00:42:45,150 --> 00:42:45,710
So,

777
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:48,000
I'll take revenge with my own hands.

778
00:42:52,510 --> 00:42:53,370
Your Highness.

779
00:42:53,880 --> 00:42:55,940
What brings you here so late at night?

780
00:42:56,110 --> 00:42:58,510
I'm here
to check on His Majesty's medicine.

781
00:42:58,510 --> 00:42:59,360
It was just finished

782
00:42:59,360 --> 00:43:00,670
and ready to be sent over.

783
00:43:00,670 --> 00:43:01,930
Flower and I are here.

784
00:43:02,360 --> 00:43:03,420
You may go and rest.

785
00:43:04,110 --> 00:43:04,550
Yes.

786
00:43:05,360 --> 00:43:06,480
The rest of you may leave as well.

787
00:43:06,480 --> 00:43:06,760
Yes.

788
00:43:06,760 --> 00:43:07,030
Yes.

789
00:43:17,280 --> 00:43:19,540
It's not too late to change your mind now.

790
00:43:21,400 --> 00:43:21,960
Put this

791
00:43:22,400 --> 00:43:23,460
into the medicine.

792
00:43:24,190 --> 00:43:25,720
Once the Emperor drinks it,

793
00:43:25,800 --> 00:43:26,800
you will survive.

794
00:43:45,840 --> 00:43:46,370
Quickly!

795
00:43:47,550 --> 00:43:48,110
Twelve.

796
00:43:51,430 --> 00:43:52,090
Don't move!

797
00:43:52,550 --> 00:43:53,830
So you knew all along!

798
00:43:55,110 --> 00:43:57,170
I had hoped my suspicions were wrong.

799
00:43:57,320 --> 00:43:58,440
Where is the antidote?

800
00:43:58,440 --> 00:43:59,550
The Qiang State's poison

801
00:43:59,550 --> 00:44:00,210
has no cure.

802
00:44:02,880 --> 00:44:03,740
Your Highness.

803
00:44:04,000 --> 00:44:05,260
Should we use torture?

804
00:44:06,920 --> 00:44:07,660
Forget it.

805
00:44:08,220 --> 00:44:09,150
She isn't lying.

806
00:44:10,510 --> 00:44:11,910
Send this packet of drugs

807
00:44:11,920 --> 00:44:12,920
to Physician Xiao

808
00:44:13,000 --> 00:44:14,210
and see if it helps.

809
00:44:14,550 --> 00:44:14,840
Yes.

810
00:44:19,410 --> 00:44:20,560
Escort me to His Majesty's place.

811
00:44:20,560 --> 00:44:21,560
There are only 2 hours left.

812
00:44:21,560 --> 00:44:22,030
Hurry.
